Package model

Class BibliographicProduct

java.lang.Object
model.BibliographicProduct
All Implemented Interfaces:
CreateID
Direct Known Subclasses:
Book, Magazine
public abstract class BibliographicProduct extends Object implements CreateID
The BibliographicProduct class contains methods and variables related to bibliographic products such as books, including their ID, name, number of pages, publication date, URL, value, amount of sales, and amount of pages read.
